DURBAN - At least 70 children have been injured after a bus reportedly overturned in KwaZulu-Natal.They were being transported to school at the time. [PICTURES] - [ADAMS MISSION] - Bus overturns leaving approximately 70 children injured. @ewnupdates @eNCA @ECR_Newswatch @_ArriveAlive pic.twitter.com/sgz82IFBWR The pupils sustained minor to moderate injuries. Paramedics found passengers climbing out of the bus, while others were walking around the scene.Some of the injured were treated at the scene before being transported to hospital.ER24 reports the accident occurred on the R603, near Adams Mission, which lies south of Durban.eNCA